## Changes to the current incentive mechanism 

https://github.com/rayonlabs/G.O.D/pull/328/files

* A beaut of a simplification to the scoring, for each comp: 1st gets 2pts, 2nd gets 1pt and everyone else gets 0, except for the bottom 25% and any duplicate submissions which get a penalty term.

* A larger test set for each job to reduce random noise
